# Lingmo OS System Configuration
#
# This directory contains core system configuration files.
# These are essential for @DISTRO_NAME@ operation.
#
# WARNING: Modifying files here may break system functionality.
# For user customizations, use /etc instead.
#
# Hierarchy:
#   /system/etc  -> Core system configs (read-only)
#   /etc         -> User/overlay configs (writable)
#
# @DISTRO_NAME@ @VERSION@ (@CODENAME@)
# Build: @BUILD_VER@ (@VERSION_TYPE@)
